        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> From eqcaster:<BR>Jedah's Choker items - This item gives a chance of not using a reagent when you cast a spell that normally would use a reagent. The items were modified so they no longer effect Enchant Metal spells, or Imbue Gem spells. The goal of the item was to save reagents used for summoning pets, casting buffs, or using Translocate fragments, not to give people a chance at a free platinum bar every time they enchanted one.</P><P>Has anyone tried this on essence emeralds?<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
